<div class="container">{{> _errors}}</div>

<div class="container" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            Register
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <form action="/register" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Username</label>
                            <input type="username" id="username" class="form-control" name="username" placeholder="Username"  value="{{username}}">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Email</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control"  placeholder="Email"  id="email" name="email" value="{{email}}">
                        </div>
                        <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Password</label>
                        <div class="input-group mb-3">
                            <input type="password" id="inputsifre"  placeholder="Password"  class="form-control" name="password">
                            <div class="input-group-append">
                                <span class="input-group-text" id="sifre"></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Register</button>
                        <br><br>
                        <hr>
                        <p>• Paralo minimum 6 karakter uzunluğunda olmalıdır.</p>
                        <p>• Username'de yalnızca harf (a-z), rakam (0-9), nokta (.), alt tire (_) kullanılabilir.</p>
                        <p>• Username büyük harf içermemelidir.</p>
                        <p>• Username, email veya password boşluk içermemelidir.</p>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>

</div>
